he roots of evil must be searched for in America. The whole world must battle with terrorism.</p><p>\"We know this better than anyone. We wish recover to all the victims and share Americans' feeling of sorrow.\"</p><div class=\"related\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/boston-marathon-explosions\">Boston Marathon bombing</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/boston\">Boston</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/massachusetts\">Massachusetts</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/usa\">United States</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/terrorism\">Global terrorism</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/chechnya\">Chechnya</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/ramzan-kadyrov\">Ramzan Kadyrov</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/instagram\">Instagram</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/us-crime\">US crime</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/dzhokhar-tsarnaev\">Dzhokhar Tsarnaev</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/tamerlan-tsarnaev\">Tamerlan Tsarnaev</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"author\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/profile/tommccarthy\">Tom McCarthy</a></div><div class=\"author\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/profile/miriam-elder\">Miriam Elder</a></div><br/><div class=\"terms\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk\">guardian.co.uk</a> &copy; 2013 Guardian News and Media Limited or its affiliated companies. All rights reserved. | Use of this content is subject to our <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/terms-of-service\">Terms & Conditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/feeds\">More Feeds</a></div><p style=\"clear:both\" />" "http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/apr/19/tsarnaev-brothers-chechnya-ramzan-kadyrov" (20849 36275) old 9 nil nil ((title nil "Chechen leader: 'The roots of evi